               Death
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the second Middlesex Jury before Mr. 
               <persName id="t17861025-41-person589">
                  BARON
                   EYRE
               <interp inst="t17861025-41-person589" type="surname" value="EYRE"></interp>
